\begin_inset Formula $W_{j}$
\end_inset

.
 Being a basis, 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{span}\{\mathbf{w}_{1},\mathbf{w}_{2},\ldots,\mathbf{w}_{j}\}$
\end_inset

 would equal 
\begin_inset Formula $W_{j}$
\end_inset

